“Gotta catch em..... what’s that?” Well, I’m glad you asked. This is @mariokemon. Mariokemon was created by the talented, @mickcrisp, and he likes to mash up Mario characters and Pokémon characters, to make a creation of his own. Who you’re seeing here is Bowstoise, a mash up of, yep, you guessed it, Bowser and Blastoise! Honestly I love this project and check the account everyday to see if a new Mariokemon was made. Right now he’s still working on the first gen Pokémon, so head on over to his page and see who or what your favorite Pokémon mashed up with. Marikart tour har äntligen kommit!

Mariokart tour är Nintendos nyaste mobilapp. Där du kör över hela världen med en ny stad varannan vecka. Den första staden vi får köra i är New York som varar de två första veckorna från lanseringen onsdagen den 25:e september. Vi vet att vi kommer få köra i Paris och Tokyo. Som jag har förstått det så kommer staden försvinna efter två veckor. Med varje stad kommer special karaktärer, bilar och fallskärmar. New Yorks är Pauline, musiker Mario, en taxi och ett plan som liknar en taxi tror jag.

Du kan styra med en hand och du väljer om du vill köra med drift eller bara svänga. Alla bilar har en power-up som ger någon sorts fördel i banorna. Sen är vissa gubbar/bilar/fallskärmar bättre på olika banor. 
Nintendo har lagt till massa gamla banor från gamla mariokart spel.

OBS! Du behöver ha ett Nintendo konto för att kunna spela.
Men dina vänner på switch som har appen kan du skicka vänförfrågan till med typ två tryck. Annars så är det vänkod som på typ alla Nintendos spel.

Om det är någon info ni saknar eller något ni vill veta om spelet så får ni gärna skriva antingen i kommentarerna eller i DM, det är bara kul.

Gå gärna med i min discord server för att kunna prata med mig och lite annat smått och gott.

caption.text:
I'm going away for a couple of days, not on holiday unfortunately. But I'll make sure to take the fun with me when I go.

2 pokemon tshirts and a Harry Potter one. Not pictured is my long sleeved skeleton tshirt (last years Halloween clothing from the kids section 😎) and also my mario pants because they are super comfy (I'm taking others too...) Those Sony headphones have lasted me 5 years odd so far and are the best I've had yet. I used to use in ear ones but for some reason can't any more. Plus I love their colour.

If you haven't read Stephen Kings memoir on writing, you should. He really cuts the bullshit in this and tells you like it is. It's a good read.

And finally but not least, the switch. Because I need to entertain a small person and myself for the best part of 48 hours, it might come in handy. Untitled goose game is going to be a yes but I really need to get back on stardew valley and complete a few quests. I'm hoping to dock it on the hotel tv but won't hold my breath.

caption.text:
What game(s) make you the most nostalgia blind?

Mine are the Gen I Pokémon games!

I honestly don't believe Red/Blue/Yellow aged that well. Objectively speaking, FireRed & LeafGreen or even Let's Go Pikachu & Eevee are superior games to the original.

However, once I turn this game on, hear the iconic music, and watch Nidorino and Gengar battle it out, I become a kid again! Hearing all the classic music, watching the battles take place with those horrible sprites, and exploring the Kanto Region is such a fantastic experience. Nostalgia mode never fails to take over and I forget all of my gripes with the games.

Being the firsts games I ever played, Pokémon Red, Blue, & Yellow hold a special place in my heart. But because of that, I am the most nostalgia blind to them! 😅
.

caption.text:
The House of the Dead revivirá de la tumba para hacer su llegada al Nintendo Switch con las primeras 2 entregas de la franquicia.

La serie es original del clásico Sega Saturn, por lo que se pensaría que el propio Sega estaría detrás de los posibles remakes, pero este no es el caso. En vez, Forever Entertainment, quienes están actualmente a cargo de los remakes de Panzer Dragoon, traerán la primera y segunda entrega de The House of the Dead al Nintendo Switch.

Dado a que la empresa está situada en Polonia, la confirmación del regreso de The House of the Dead está en polaco.

Dicho esto, todavía no se puede decir con certeza si sea un remake o reboot, pero lo más probable sean remakes, ya que las primeras dos entregas regresarán de la misma manera que Panzer Dragon lo hará.

Por el momento, The House of the Dead 1 y 2 llegarán para Nintendo Switch en el 2020, y se desconoce si estarán disponibles en otras plataformas.

Developer : Nintendo Co. Ltd

Seri permainan balap yang menjadi unggulan di konsol Nintendo Switch hadir resmi di Smartphone kalian!

Grafik yang memukau serta gameplay dengan segudang fitur membuat game ini layak ada di Smartphone anda. Gameplay dari seri Mario Kart Tour ini mengingatkan admin kepada game Crash Team Racing / CTR karena disini kalian akan balapan dan dapat saling melempar senjata atau menaruh trap yang didapat dari box dan di sebar di sepanjang permainan.

Sedikit poin minus dari game ini ialah hanya dapat dimainkan di mode Potrait dan belum ada fitur Multiplayer. Untuk fitur multiplayer sendiri akan hadir di next update

De 1859 com as cartas "Hanafuda", seguindo até 1981 com o jogo Donkey Kong, onde foi a primeira aparição de Mario com o nome de Jumpman, até os dias atuais com Super mario Odyssey e o mais recente Mario Kat tour, a Nintendo completou 130 anos esse mês. Muitos dizem que a empresa é fraca diante da Sony com seu Playstation e da Microsoft com seu Xbox one, mas a verdade é que ela ano após ano vem trazendo novidades na maneira de se jogar vídeo game, sempre inovando no quesito experiência do jogador. Quem não se lembra do primeiro portátil, do seu primeiro sensor de movimento, do 3D sem óculos e do recente console híbrido!! São 130 anos de cenários belos, grandes aventuras, músicas que ficam na cabeça não importa quando tempo passe e de mínimos detalhes que superam muitas vezes qualquer poder gráfico e permite a cada jogador viver o mesmo jogo de maneiras diferentes. Fica aqui minha homenagem a essa grande empresa que fez e faz parte da vida de muita gente! Parabéns Nintendo 🎁🎊🎉

caption.text:
[Leave my Papa alone!]⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Mario was on a quest, a self made one however, he was on the search for the Yoshi that saved both him and Luigi's life when they were merely two infants. He wanted to find him and simply thank him for everything, how probably wouldn't have been where he is without that Yoshi keeping him safe. He also wanted to apologize for all the trouble, and possibly all of the crying...⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Mario went back into Yoshi's Island with the use of a pipe that Toadsworth mentioned to him. Getting onto the island, the smell of it gave him major nostalgia. The smell of the forests, and the smell of all the fruit being eaten by all the Yoshi's on the island. He looked around to see if he could find That one exact Yoshi.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Mario spent hours trying to find it but with no prevail. "Maybe this was-a bad idea... I can't find him, because there's just so many of them that happen to be green!" Mario said eating on an apple, he could see why the dinosaurs loved these apples as they were really juicy, crisp and sweet.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Mario heard a cry of a Yoshi, it sounded like it was in trouble. Mario not wanting to ignore the plea for help, he ran over into the forests to follow the cries of the Yoshi. Seeing the Yoshi being surrounded by a group of Kameks and Hammer bros. They were ready to strike, Mario ran over to the Yoshi, this one looked a bit older as it was developing some wrinkles.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
But as Mario ran, he took a good look at the Yoshi and he stopped as a memory went through his mind. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
//Mario's mind and memories...//⁣⁣⁣
A Yoshi found a crying baby with a little red hat and titled its head making a confused noise. "... Yoshi?" The dinosaur was shocked seeing a human baby on his own so not taking too much time, he picked up the baby and began comforting him, like he would a baby Yoshi. When little Baby Mario would stop crying he looked up and simply said words as best as he could. "P-Papa...?" The Yoshi smiled and cradled the baby, he had a responsibilty now and that gave his life purpose. Yoshi placed Baby Mario on his back, beginning his search for baby Luigi. (Story continued in comments!)
